divs: Sighting DetailsI saw an "H" shaped object in the sky as I was coming home from work and was stopped at a stop sign and noticed the craft in the sky. There was 4 white lights on the near side and at least 2 white lights on the far side with a red light in the middle. I continued to drive slow but lost sight of it behind the trees that lined the street. The craft just seemed to hover in the sky. The craft reminded me of a tie fighter from Star Wars.
